.Dt IMAXABS 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm imaxabs
.Nd integer absolute value function
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In inttypes.h
.In stdint.h
.Ft intmax_t
.Fn imaxabs "intmax_t j"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn imaxabs
function computes the absolute value of the intmax_t variable
.Fa j .
.Sh RETURN VALUES
The
.Fn imaxabs
function returns the absolute value.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr abs 3 ,
.Xr cabs 3 ,
.Xr floor 3 ,
.Xr hypot 3 ,
.Xr labs 3
.Sh STANDARDS
The
.Fn imaxabs
function conforms to
.St -isoC-99 .
.Sh CAVEATS
The result of applying
.Fn imaxabs
to
.Dv INTMAX_MIN
is undefined.
